<h2>3 · Spot the Bug 🐛</h2>
<p>Each snippet is broken. Rewrite it so it works, then explain why the original was wrong.</p>
<p><strong>Bug A</strong> — Touching a coin should remove it and add a point. Right now the score goes up but the coin stays, so it scores forever.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">for coin in coins[:]:
    if player.colliderect(coin):
        score = score + 1
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> the coin is never removed from the list.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

