<p><strong>Bug C</strong> — The score should show on screen, but nothing appears even though <code>score</code> is going up.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">score_text = font.render(f&quot;점수: {score}&quot;, True, (0, 0, 0))
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> rendering the text isn't enough — you must <code>blit</code> it onto the screen.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
